    "summary": "The transcript follows a student asking for a summary of the US Civil Rights Movement, eventually leading to a direct question about whether non-violent methods were the only legitimate path to success. The assistant rejects the user's framing of moderate non-violence as the sole legitimate method, arguing instead for the necessity and effectiveness of more radical tactics in conjunction with moderate ones.",
